# Project Agent Rules

Read `AGENTS.md` and `CLAUDE.md` before substantial changes.

- Respond to the user in Spanish unless they explicitly request another language.
- Write Git commit messages and PR titles/descriptions in English.
- Use `resources/ts`; do not recreate `resources/js`.
- Reuse existing Actions, Services, Form Requests, Policies, Enums, DTOs, Resources, ViewModels, and shared TS components.
- Keep public routes and business rules unchanged unless explicitly requested.
- Run the smallest useful check while editing. Before merge to `Dev`, run `./scripts/ci-check-docker.sh`.
- Never leak secrets, tokens, raw exception messages, SQL/filesystem errors, or private user data.
